data.description: Stately and gracious, this nearly 4000 sq ft, custom 4BR, 3BA ranch sits on a large corner property in gated Millstone Landing.  Updates include crown moldings, impact windows, hurricane screens on back patio, newer central air (2021), plantation shutters, granite counters, SS appliances and gleaming wood laminate floors.  Soaring ceilings, split BR plan, Mst BR with office/den, walk in closet, amazing bath with soaker tub, sep shower, and amazing screened porch w/separate back garden area and fenced side yard.  Community has newer clubhouse, pool, tennis, basketball, community room and more.  Low HOA dues. No age restrictions, newer community...great location!
